title: Open format followed by budget model presentation (University of Delaware)
text: ( Source : University of Delaware ) 3:14 p.m., Sept . 30 , 2015--All University of Delaware students, faculty and staff are invited to meet with Provost Domenico Grasso in an open-format, town hall meeting scheduled from 4-5:30 p.m., Tuesday,
